    <item>
      <title>美国立法者希望禁止芯片法案获胜者使用中国工具</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/lawmakers-look-to-bar-chips-act-winners-from-using-chinese-tools</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国立法者希望阻止获得联邦芯片制造基金的公司在政府支持的工厂使用中国制造的设备，这是限制北京对国内芯片生产影响的努力的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/lawmakers-look-to-bar-chips-act-winners-from-using-chinese-tools</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Pritzker 选择 IBM 和 Discover 竞购联邦量子基金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/pritzker-taps-ibm-discover-in-bid-for-federal-quantum-funds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊利诺伊州州长 J.B. Pritzker 已向包括国际商业机器公司和 Discover Financial Services 在内的财团寻求帮助，以赢得联邦资金来开发量子技术。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/pritzker-taps-ibm-discover-in-bid-for-federal-quantum-funds</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 14:50:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民意调查显示工党在苏格兰领先优势下滑至四个百分点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-18/labour-lead-in-scotland-slips-to-four-points-poll-suggests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项新的民意调查显示，工党在苏格兰对苏格兰民族党的领先优势已从 10 个百分点下滑至 4 个百分点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-18/labour-lead-in-scotland-slips-to-four-points-poll-suggests</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 14:12:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亿万富翁拉特克利夫称英国已“受够”苏纳克领导的保守党</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/billionaire-ratcliffe-says-uk-has-had-enough-of-sunak-s-tories</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国第二大富豪吉姆·拉特克利夫在下个月大选临近尾声之际表示，英国人已经“受够了”首相里希·苏纳克领导的保守党执政，并“准备好迎接改变”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/billionaire-ratcliffe-says-uk-has-had-enough-of-sunak-s-tories</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 14:11:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>奈杰尔·法拉奇威胁加剧，凯尔·斯塔默猛烈抨击“没有资金”的改革宣言</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/starmer-slams-unfunded-reform-manifesto-as-farage-uk-election-threat-grows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基尔·斯塔默指责前脱欧活动家奈杰尔·法拉奇向英国选民做出了英国无法承受的承诺，民意调查显示，这可能成为未来五年的一场关键政治斗争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/starmer-slams-unfunded-reform-manifesto-as-farage-uk-election-threat-grows</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 12:17:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
