    <item>
      <title>南非股市飙升暗示投票后市场情绪出现转变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/usd-zar-south-africa-stocks-rand-surge-on-government-of-national-unity-gnu</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非股市基准指数今年涨幅最大，表明在经历了三年来最长的单日资金流出后，投资者对该国股市的看法开始转为乐观。兰特和政府债券价格飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/usd-zar-south-africa-stocks-rand-surge-on-government-of-national-unity-gnu</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 10:59:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
